==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blind mans buff
<hw>Blind" man's buff"</hw></mhw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>. <ety>[See <er>Buff</er> a buffet.]</ety> <def>A game in
which one person is blindfolded, and tries to catch some one of the
other players, and tell who it is.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Surely he fancies I play at <qex>blindman's buff</qex> with him,
for he thinks I never have my eyes open.</q>
<rj><qau>Stillingfleet.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blindman's holiday</ent>⟦br⟧
